* [Cowsay package](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/cowsay/vignettes/cowsay_tutorial.html) - Speaking animals :cow: :monkey:

```{r cowsay, echo=TRUE, warning=FALSE}
say("Hello world!", "cow")
say("Hello you!", "monkey")
```

* [Fortunes package](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/fortunes/vignettes/fortunes.pdf) - Collected Wisdom :bulb: in <i class="fab fa-r-project" style="color:blue"></i>

```{r echo=FALSE, warning=FALSE}
library(fortunes)
fortune(6)

fortune(68)

fortune(92)

fortune(192)

fortune(326)
```